The Australian New Zealand Spontaneous Coronary Artery Dissection (ANZ-SCAD) 
Registry - A Multi-Centre Cohort Study: Protocol, Background and Significance.

Kim SK(1), Wing-Lun E(2), Chandrasekhar J(3), Puri A(4), Burgess S(5), Ford 
TJ(6), Kovacic J(7), Graham RM(8), Psaltis PJ(9), Zaman S(10).

