The role of nutrition in harnessing the immune system: a potential approach to 
prevent cancer.

Xiaogang H(1), Sharma M(2)(3), Saif I(2)(3), Ali G(2)(3), Li X(2), Salama ES(4).

Author information:
(1)Pingliang Rehabilitation Center Hospital, No. 23 Taitong Road, Kongtong 
District, Pingliang, 744000, People's Republic of China.
(2)MOE, Key Laboratory of Cell Activities and Stress Adaptations, Lanzhou 
University, Lanzhou City, 730000, Gansu Province, People's Republic of China.
(3)Department of Occupational and Environmental Health, School of Public Health, 
